and get ready for him.

624
00:52:21,445 --> 00:52:24,448
If my husband never returns,

625
00:52:24,448 --> 00:52:30,821
I'll be chaste until I die.

626
00:52:30,821 --> 00:52:33,356
So please reconsider.

627
00:52:33,356 --> 00:52:39,863
A chaste courtesan's
daughter is ridiculous.

628
00:52:39,863 --> 00:52:43,100
