629
00:52:43,100 --> 00:52:47,093
Be it your mother or I,
fidelity is the same.

630
00:52:47,437 --> 00:52:49,740
But does class make us different?

631
00:52:49,740 --> 00:52:53,744
What?

632
00:52:53,744 --> 00:52:57,737
