A wife is loyal to one husband.

633
00:52:55,612 --> 00:53:05,655
But would you fall on your knees,

634
00:53:05,655 --> 00:53:10,427
and serve two kings, governor?

635
00:53:10,427 --> 00:53:13,797
How dare you!

636
00:53:13,797 --> 00:53:17,501
You will die for that!

637
00:53:17,501 --> 00:53:21,494
Drag her outside!

638
00:53:21,304 --> 00:53:25,297
