you disobeyed my orders.

641
00:53:35,318 --> 00:53:38,789
So you deserve to die!

642
00:53:38,789 --> 00:53:45,695
Did I steal food?

643
00:53:45,695 --> 00:53:49,466
Did I disobey my mother,
or cheat my fellow brethren?

644
00:53:49,466 --> 00:53:52,803
If not,
then why are you punishing me?

645
00:53:52,803 --> 00:53:56,796
You must be ignorant of our laws.

646
00:53:59,910 --> 00:54:03,446
Then tell me what law I've broken.

647
