658
00:00:29,109 --> 00:00:33,102
Chunhyang, write as I say.

659
00:00:31,111 --> 00:00:35,115
As a lowly courtesan,
I disobeyed the governor,

660
00:00:35,115 --> 00:00:39,108
so I deserve to die for my crime.

661
00:00:40,120 --> 00:00:44,113
"One Love"

662
00:00:43,123 --> 00:00:46,126
Chief Executioner!

663
00:00:46,126 --> 00:00:51,131
Yes, sir.

664
00:00:51,131 --> 00:00:58,138
Beat her till her organs burst!

665
